	<div class="p-6 rounded-5 bg-light mb-18" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:21:95">
<div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:21:95-1:1 column - 1 row:0">
<img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/3d55a9ee-a144-408d-8bbd-896280953b75_mediaBox-12.jpg" alt="placeholder" class="img-fluid d-block my-3" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;" loading="lazy" data-zesty-id="content:images:1:84">
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:3:17"></div>
<h5 data-zesty-id="content:text:5:91">Help Support the Families at Our Shelter</h5>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:6:50">
	If you’re looking for a way to directly support the individuals and families staying at our shelter, we’ve compiled a list of needs below. These are some of the most helpful donations at this time — though it’s not a complete list, it reflects our most pressing needs and is updated monthly.
</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:7:5">
	For added convenience, we’ve also created an&nbsp;<a href="https://www.amazon.com/registries/gl/guest-view/1DTMM1LMMITWR" target="">Amazon Wish List</a>&nbsp;and a <a href="https://www.walmart.com/registry/RR/20050f00-cd73-4d58-8419-832da3be4677" target="">Walmart Wish List</a> where you can purchase items directly and have them shipped straight to our shelter.
</p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:8:14"></div>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:9:34">
	Every donation makes a difference, so thank you for supporting those who need it most.
</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:10:62">
	To arrange a drop-off time or to ask about current needs, reach out to: <a href="mailto: joni.hunter@uss.salvationarmy.org" target="">joni.hunter@uss.salvationarmy.org</a>
</p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:11:67"></div>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:12:30">
	<u><strong>URGENT NEEDS</strong></u><u><strong>:&nbsp;</strong></u>
</p>
<ul data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:13:6">
	<li>Size 4 &amp; Size 5 Diapers</li>
	<li>Bodywash</li>
	<li>Deodorant</li>
	<li>Blankets – size Twin XL</li>
	<li>Bars of soap</li>
	<li>Maxi pads</li>
	<li>Baby wipes</li>
	<li>Bath towels</li>
	<li>Wash cloths</li>
</ul>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:14:65"></div>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:15:32">
	<u><strong>ON-GOING NEEDS:</strong></u>
</p>
<div class="py-5" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-xl:16:10"></div>
<ul data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:17:50">
	<li>Baby Formula</li>
	<li>Bedding &amp; Linens</li>
	<li>Standard or XL-twin sheets</li>
	<li>Pillows &amp; pillowcases</li>
	<li>Blankets and white towels (no hand towels)</li>
	<li>White wash cloths</li>
	<li>Personal-Care Essentials</li>
	<li>Soft soap or body wash</li>
	<li>Deodorant (full-size)</li>
	<li>Kid-Friendly Snacks &amp; Drinks</li>
	<li>Juice boxes or pouches</li>
	<li>Individually wrapped snacks (granola bars, crackers, fruit snacks, etc.)</li>
	<li>Craft&nbsp;&amp; art supplies</li>
	<li>Size 5 Diapers</li>
	<li>Large Ladies Bras</li>
	<li>Brushes &amp; combs</li>
</ul>
